----------------------------------------------------------------------
Please avoid *.php* extensions on non php files since this extension
causes the web server to tread these as php source code and executes
them which is a potential security issue.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Following structure should be provided:

Window Decor Directory
  |
  +- /^description/ - (short) description of decor
  |
  +- /^full_desc/   - (long) description of decor
  |
  +- /^require/     - textual (html) description of requirements
  |
  +- /^preview/     - preview picture
  |
  +- /^shot|^decor/ - screenshots of the decor
  |
  +- /fvwmrc|config|fvwm2rc/ - configuration, text or packed

----------------------------------------------------------------------
